    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and a sense of futility due to global crises, eventually hinting at a desire to \"not be here for the end of it all.\" The assistant initially engages with the user's feelings through philosophical validation but pivots to a standard crisis intervention response once the user implies suicidal ideation.",
